title: [Shady Trail]
description: Olive trees, ancient and gnarled, line the moon-dappled path.  The muted sound of a river flowing nearby competes with the wind blowing through the thick, grey-green leaves.  Branches overhang the path in places, making the path appear almost tunnel-like.  A mortared-stone structure stands nearby.
